high_descs: Turn right and walk down the passage and reach the bathroom on the left and reach the bathtub.
Pick up the butterknife from the tub.
Turn around to head out of the bathroom and turn left to reach the bread box.
Cut the bread in the box.
Turn around to walk down the passage and head to the fridge on the right.
Put the butterknife in the fridge.
Turn around to exit the kitchen and turn left to head down the passage and reach the bread box.
Pick up a slice of bread from the box.
Turn around to head down the passage and turn right to reach the microwave in the kitchen.
Heat the bread in the microwave and take it out.
Turn left to head to the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Bread in the Fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the bathtub.
Take the butterknife from the tub.
Turn around and go near the bread.
Cut the bread into slices using the knife.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the butterknife into the fridge.
Turn around and go near the bread.
Take the slice of bread from the bread box.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the bread slice into the microwave oven.
Then take it out and go near the fridge.
Put the bread into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the bread into the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the bathtub on your right, going all the way down and entering the last door on the left.
Pick up the butterknife from the bathtub.
Exit this room how you came in and turn left to the bread on the ground.
Slice the bread in the box.
Turn around and walk down the hall until reaching the kitchen area on the right, then head to the fridge in the corner.
Place the butterknife in the fridge.
Return to the box with the sliced bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Return to the kitchen and head to the microwave on the counters.
Use the microwave on the slice of bread and pick the bread back up.
Turn back to the fridge to your left.
Place the bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of Bread in a Fridge.
